quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  57,19,aur jo log khuda aur is ke payghambaroon par imaan laaye yahi apne perwar-digaar ke nazdeek Seddiq aur shaheed hain. un ke liye un ( ke aamaal ) ka sila hoga. aur un ( ke imaan ) ki roshni. aur jin logon ne kufarkiya aur hamari aayton ko jhtlaya wohi ahal dozakh hain
  57,20,jaan rakho ke duniya ki zindagi mehez khail aur tamasha aur zeenat ( vaaraysh ) aur tumahray aapas mein fakhr ( vstaysh ) aur maal o aulaad ki aik dosray se ziyada talab ( o khawhish ) hai ( is ki misaal aisi hai ) jaisay barish ke ( is se khaiti ugti aur ) kisanon ko khaiti bhali lagti hai phir woh khoob zor par aati hai phir ( ae dekhnay walay ) to is ko daikhta hai ke ( pick kar ) zard par jati hai phir choora choora hojati hai aur akhirat mein ( kafiroon ke liye ) azaab shadeed aur ( mominoun ke liye ) khuda ki taraf se bakhshish aur khushnodi hai. aur duniya ki zindagi to mata fraib hai
  57,21,( Bandoo ) apne perwar-digaar ki bakhshish ki taraf aur jannat ki ( taraf ) jis ka arz aasman aur zameen ke arz ka sa hai. aur jo un logon ke liye tayyar ki gayi hai jo khuda par aur is ke payghambaroon par imaan laaye hain lapko. yeh khuda ka fazl hai jisay chahay ataa farmaiye. aur khuda barray fazl ka maalik hai
  57,22,koi museebat malik par aur khud tum par nahi padtee magar peshtar is ke ke hum is ko peda karen aik kitaab mein ( likhi hui ) hai. ( aur ) yeh ( kaam ) khuda ko aasaan hai
  57,23,taakay jo ( matlab ) tum se faut hogaya ho is ka gham nah khaya karo aur jo tum ko is ne diya ho is par itrayea nah karo. aur khuda kisi itranay aur shekhi bigharnay walay ko dost nahi rakhta
  57,24,jo khud bhi bukhal karen aur logon ko bhi bukhal skhayin aur jo shakhs rogrdani kere to khuda bhi be parwa ( aur ) wohi sazawar hamd ( وثنا ) hai
